getArcTokensCompletingJoin

public List<ArcToken> getArcTokensCompletingJoin()
Description copied from interface: JoinResult
Returns the ArcTokens which were required to complete this join, and will be considered the parents of the new NodeToken. If JoinResult.isJoinComplete() would return false, this method should throw an IllegalStateException.
